description: The Greek myDATA v1.0.8 provided by AADE is in a single dll. Get full control and support from myDATA. It offers a number of simple tools that make creating apps that support myDATA simple and quick.
releaseNotes:
The updated myDATA version 1.0.8 is now available in the library. More specifically:
	A. Class SendInvoices
	     1. The structure "address" has been added.
	     2. The method "newAddress" has been added.
	     3. The structure "deliveryNoteAddress" has been added.
	     4. The method "newDeliveryNoteAddress" has been added.
	     5. In the "elements" structure, the field "noteAddress" has been added.
	
	B. Class RequestInvoices
	     1. If the invoice additionally includes a delivery note, the getInvoices function returns the required indication.
	     2. The structure of "invoice" has been modified. New fields have been added to almost every structure of the invoice.
	     3. The method "getPaymentMethods" also returns the structures "ProviderSignature" and "ECRToken".
	     4. The ability to return AADE errors in Greek or English has been added.
	
	C. Class RequestMyExpenses, RequestMyIncome, RequestInvoicesProvider, RequestReceiverInfoProvider
	     1. The ability to return AADE errors in Greek or English has been added.
	
	D. Class myDATATools
	     1. The methods getMeasurmentUnit, getMovePurpose, getVatCategory, and getValidCategory return the newest values.
	
	E. The class VivaWalletPOS has been added.
	
	F. The class SendPaymentMethod has been added.
	
	G. New ERP Code Samples:
	     1. Type 1.1 - Invoice Delivery Note
		 2. Type 1.1 - Invoice Delivery Note Custom
		 3. Type 1.1 - Payment with POS
		 4. Type 9.3 - Unrelated Movement Document
		 5. SendPaymentMethod - Single Payment
		 6. SendPaymentMethod - Mixed Payment
	
	H. New Provider Code Samples
	     1. Type 1.1 - Invoice Delivery Note
		 2. Type 1.1 - Invoice Delivery Note Custom
		 3. Type 1.1 - Payment with POS
		 4. Type 9.3 - Unrelated Movement Document
